OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1779563472
OL,3,CMan, 95, died after care home assault
OL,4,Cand left without water at hospital
OL,6,FA 95-year-old man who died after being
OL,7,Fassaulted by a fellow care home
OL,8,Fresident was left without water while
OL,9,Fbeing treated in hospital, an inquest
OL,10,Fhas heard.
OL,12,FThe Coroner was told that Douglas
OL,13,FDavies, who had been living at
OL,14,FLakeside Manor in St Peter, was
OL,15,Fattacked in the care home's lounge on
OL,16,F29 August 2023, suffering a broken hip.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1779563472
OL,3,CMan, 95, died after care home assault
OL,4,Cand left without water at hospital
OL,6,FHis subsequent treatment at Jersey
OL,7,FGeneral Hospital included multiple
OL,8,Ffailings, the inquest heard, such as a
OL,9,Flack of proper nutrition and necessary
OL,10,Fantibiotics.
OL,12,FMr Davies underwent emergency hip
OL,13,Fsurgery the following day, but was
OL,14,Fthen found to have an acute kidney
OL,15,Finjury following blood tests.
OL,17,FHe then stopped eating and drinking
OL,18,Fbefore dying on 4 September 2023.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1779563472
OL,3,CMan, 95, died after care home assault
OL,4,Cand left without water at hospital
OL,6,FA postmortem revealed that Mr Davies
OL,7,Fdied as a result of multiple organ
OL,8,Ffailure caused by complications from
OL,9,Fthe hip surgery, and that his old age
OL,10,Fand dementia were contributing factors.
OL,12,FA serious incident investigation
OL,13,Freport carried out by Health and Care
OL,14,FJersey (HCJ) found that the day after
OL,15,FMr Davies was admitted to hospital,
OL,16,Fthere was no record of him receiving
OL,17,Fany fluids.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1779563472
OL,3,CMan, 95, died after care home assault
OL,4,Cand left without water at hospital
OL,6,FThe review states there was "no
OL,7,Fconsideration" for the frail man's
OL,8,Fnutrition during his six-day stay in
OL,9,Fhospital and no proper supervision by
OL,10,Fsenior managers.
OL,12,FIt was noted that Mr Davies also
OL,13,Fsuffered a morphine overdose during
OL,14,Fhis treatment, for which he needed
OL,15,Femergency care.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1779563472
OL,3,CMan, 95, died after care home assault
OL,4,Cand left without water at hospital
OL,6,FStaffing concerns were raised at the
OL,7,Finquest, with agency workers
OL,8,Ffrequently used to fill gaps caused by
OL,9,Fabsence - on more than one occasion
OL,10,Fwhilst Mr Davies was in hospital, some
OL,11,Fshifts were not covered.
OL,13,FDr Simon Chapman, an emergency
OL,14,Fmedicine consultant at the hospital,
OL,15,Ftold the inquest their care "fell
OL,16,Fshort".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1779563472
OL,3,CMan, 95, died after care home assault
OL,4,Cand left without water at hospital
OL,6,FHe explained that doctors and nurses
OL,7,Fhad not even considered the
OL,8,Fpossibility of kidney damage when Mr
OL,9,FDavies was taken to hospital, meaning
OL,10,Fhe would have been more likely to
OL,11,Foverdose on opioids.
OL,13,FSpeaking about what has been done to
OL,14,Favoid similar failings moving forward,
OL,15,Fthe consultant said that the hospital
OL,16,Fnow uses a fully digital system for
OL,17,Fall staff to share notes on patients
OL,18,Fand better identify those who need
OL,19,Fmore serious treatment.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1779563472
OL,3,CMan, 95, died after care home assault
OL,4,Cand left without water at hospital
OL,6,FSimon West, Medical Director for HCJ,
OL,7,Fsays: "I would like to offer my
OL,8,Fdeepest sympathies to Mr Davies'
OL,9,Ffamily.
OL,11,F"Following this case, several measures
OL,12,Fhave been implemented, and I'd like to
OL,13,Ffurther reassure islanders that as an
OL,14,Forganisation we are firmly committed
OL,15,Fto the continuous enhancement of
OL,16,Fpatient care.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1779563472
OL,3,CMan, 95, died after care home assault
OL,4,Cand left without water at hospital
OL,6,F"We also continue to strengthen our
OL,7,Fapproach to supporting patients'
OL,8,Fhydration and nutritional needs as a
OL,9,Ffundamental part of safe and
OL,10,Fcompassionate care across all our
OL,11,Fservices."
OL,13,FAs Jersey goes to the polls and with
OL,14,FSenators back on the ballot, ITV
OL,15,FChannel's Jess Dunsdon and Luke
OL,16,FKeohane break down the key election
OL,17,Fissues alongside expert guests. Listen
OL,18,Fto Jersey Votes wherever you get your
OL,19,Fpodcasts or watch on ITVX, and YouTube
OL,20,Fbelow, with new episodes each
OL,21,FThursday...
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/8
